summary: Adds a few NPCs to the world, voiced by me and my wife.
descriptionHtml:
This mod adds a few NPCs to the world, fully voiced by me and my wife. This is a on-going project. So expect more NPCs in the future. So far I have added four NPCs. They can be found around Riverwood, and the outskirts of Whiterun.

This mod is only for immersion purposes. They don\'t have any quests at the moment, only a story to tell. 

/tomme25

Please tell me if something isn\'t working as it should!
